{"tid":1198051,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"12號 唔好散就得","createTime":"2019-06-10T06:30:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T14:37:50.000Z","uid":34626,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"36524b45603517116db7088bf4e531e3a0a00e68","tid":1198051,"uid":34626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T06:30:24.000Z","msg":"好多人琴日行完就散<br />\n大台講野又廢 搞到大部分人頹曬走左<br />\n<br />\n12號有琴日十分一人數留守<br />\n啲狗都做唔倒啲咩 唔洗衝都易守好多<br />\n<br />\n寧願你係橋食花生都唔好散<br />\n一散左就越黎越少人<br />\n<br />\n大家加油呀！"},{"pid":"e198cc7403ed73f05a0af9232bd48ab59f939260","tid":1198051,"uid":130976,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T06:32:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xiy5OTL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXiy5OTL.png&h=6bf47e15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係11號</span></span>"},{"pid":"5e4a2316886ebc71799f4beb76c764481753ce84","tid":1198051,"uid":34626,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"e198cc7403ed73f05a0af9232bd48ab59f939260","tid":1198051,"uid":130976,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T06:32:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xiy5OTL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXiy5OTL.png&h=6bf47e15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係11號</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T06:37:19.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />sorry<br />\n<br />\n不過真係背水一戰啦屌 琴日士氣雖然唔好<br />\n11號晚唔好再理大台啲on9 頂硬上"},{"pid":"58174e094d394e1bb8659d26bb6e9332efc515f5","tid":1198051,"uid":238415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T06:39:08.000Z","msg":"港豬依家既思維係<br />\n唔散 = 搞事"},{"pid":"745c2ccf02611825f2e8dab9371ee91e74c8ec13","tid":1198051,"uid":34626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"58174e094d394e1bb8659d26bb6e